walking down a street at night

00:03:44.410 --> 00:03:47.440
in one of the most
vibrant city in the world,

00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:50.410
only to find it's eerily quiet.

00:03:50.410 --> 00:03:52.900
There are no lights on in the
houses because, well, nobody

00:03:52.900 --> 00:03:53.580
is home.

00:03:53.580 --> 00:03:54.471
